      <title outputclass="H3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">8.1104</ph> Contract
clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body" outputclass="Body" class="- topic/p ">Insert
the following clauses in solicitations and contracts for leasing
of motor vehicles, unless the motor vehicles are leased in foreign
countries:</p>
         <ol id="d521e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d529e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                   The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062379.dita#i1062379"
                        base="i1062379"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-4</xref>,
Vehicle Lease Payments.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d529e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                   The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062392.dita#i1062392"
                        base="i1062392"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-5</xref>,
Condition of Leased Vehicles.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d529e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                   The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062403.dita#i1062403"
                        base="i1062403"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-6</xref>,
Marking of Leased Vehicles.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d529e56" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                   A clause substantially the same
as the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062413.dita#i1062413"
                        base="i1062413"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-7</xref>, Tagging of Leased Vehicles,
for vehicles leased over 60 days <ph rev="FAC 2019-02 March 27, 2019" class="- topic/ph ">(see <?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 8.1104 by removing from paragraph (d) “(see subpart B of 41 CFR 102-34)” and adding “(see subpart B of 41 CFR part 102-34)” in its place.?>subpart B <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] Technical Amendments?>of 41 CFR
part 102-34)</ph>.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d529e75" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                   The provisions and clauses prescribed
elsewhere in the FAR for solicitations and contracts for supplies
when a fixed-price contract is contemplated, but excluding-</p>
               <ol id="d521e74" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d529e85" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                         The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1063103.dita#i1063103"
                              base="i1063103"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.211-16</xref>,
Variation in Quantity;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d529e97" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                         The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049385.dita#i1049385"
                              base="i1049385"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-1</xref>,
Payments;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d529e109" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                         The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055699.dita#i1055699"
                              base="i1055699"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-20</xref>,
Contracts for Materials, Supplies, Articles, and Equipment Exceeding
$15,000; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d529e121" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                         The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1047139.dita#i1047139"
                              base="i1047139"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.246-16</xref>,
Responsibility for Supplies.</p>
                     <p id="d529e130" class="- topic/p "/>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
